Coos,

June, 1895. Holmes v. Holmes. Writ of Entry, to foreclose a mortgage. Facts found by a referee. Bingham, Mitchell Batchellor and Ladd f Fletcher, for the plaintiff. Bingham Bingham and Drew, Jordan f Buckley, for the defendant. Chase, J.

The reserved case presents no question of law that is insisted upon.

Conditional judgment on the report in favor of the pluintiff.

All concurred.
